    </exercise><exercise id="fs-id1575776" type="problems-exercises"><problem id="fs-id1910129">    <para id="import-auto-id1857082">Waves on a swimming pool propagate at 0.750 m/s. You splash the water at one end of the pool and observe the wave go to the opposite end, reflect, and return in 30.0 s. How far away is the other end of the pool?</para>
