    </exercise><exercise id="fs-id1409377" type="problems-exercises"><problem id="fs-id1412413">    <para id="import-auto-id2382162">How many times a minute does a boat bob up and down on ocean waves that have a wavelength of 40.0 m and a propagation speed of 5.00 m/s?</para>
